      <title>Robinhood 计划为交易者提供期货、指数期权交易机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/robinhood-plans-to-give-traders-access-to-futures-index-options</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗宾汉市场公司 (Robinhood Markets Inc.) 正在扩大其期货交易和指数期权产品范围，因为这家零售经纪公司旨在吸引更多成熟投资者使用其平台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/robinhood-plans-to-give-traders-access-to-futures-index-options</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果与中国比亚迪秘密合作开发长续航电动汽车电池</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/apple-secretly-worked-with-china-s-byd-on-long-range-ev-battery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，苹果公司多年来一直与中国汽车制造商比亚迪股份有限公司合作，作为其现已取消的汽车项目的一部分，开发长续航电池，为当今使用的技术奠定了基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/apple-secretly-worked-with-china-s-byd-on-long-range-ev-battery</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 22:03:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果首席人才官上任不到两年即将离职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/apple-s-chief-people-officer-to-exit-after-less-than-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，苹果公司首席人才官在任职不到两年后即将离职，这对于公司高管的任期而言异常短暂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/apple-s-chief-people-officer-to-exit-after-less-than-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 20:02:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谷歌利用核能寻找新能源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/google-goes-nuclear-in-search-for-new-energy-sources-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着越来越多的科技公司为人工智能寻找新的动力来源，谷歌能源与气候高级总监迈克尔·特雷尔 (Michael Terrell) 也参与讨论该公司在核能方面的最新投资。他在《彭博科技》节目中与 Ed Ludlow 和 Caroline Hyde 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/google-goes-nuclear-in-search-for-new-energy-sources-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 19:28:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>蜂窝空间竞赛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/the-cellular-space-race-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[AST SpaceMobile 总裁 Scott Wisniewski 讨论了该公司的网络扩张计划，与 SpaceX 等公司展开竞争。他在“彭博科技”节目中与 Ed Ludlow 和 Caroline Hyde 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-16/the-cellular-space-race-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 19:27:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Jump Trading 在游戏开发商的诉讼中被指控“哄抬股价并抛售”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/jump-trading-accused-of-pump-and-dump-in-game-developer-s-suit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[视频游戏开发商 FractureLabs 对 Jump Trading 提起诉讼，指控加密货币行业最大的做市商之一通过操纵网络游戏中使用的代币价格进行“欺诈和欺骗”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/jump-trading-accused-of-pump-and-dump-in-game-developer-s-suit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 19:17:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏丹国民被指控参与“匿名苏丹”网络攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/sudanese-nationals-indicted-for-alleged-anonymous-sudan-roles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名苏丹国民因涉嫌参与“匿名苏丹”组织而被美国检察官起诉，该组织对美国政府机构、机场和洛杉矶一家大型医院发动网络攻击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/sudanese-nationals-indicted-for-alleged-anonymous-sudan-roles</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 17:42:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Airbnb 推出联合房东市场，增加房源供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/airbnb-launches-co-host-marketplace-to-boost-listing-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Airbnb Inc. 在其应用程序和网站上推出了一个新功能，房主可以雇佣其他房东来管理他们的出租房屋，此举凸显了增加房源数量和吸引更多人使用该平台的更广泛努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/airbnb-launches-co-host-marketplace-to-boost-listing-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国国家相关机构呼吁调查英特尔安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/china-state-linked-agency-calls-for-probe-into-intel-security</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国互联网监管机构支持的一家机构正在推动对国内销售的英特尔公司产品进行调查，并警告其存在安全漏洞和高故障率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/china-state-linked-agency-calls-for-probe-into-intel-security</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 10:54:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
