      <title>新兴市场开始意识到特朗普风险，墨西哥比索表现落后</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/chip-stocks-sink-em-index-as-china-eyes-correction-territory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员在下个月美国大选前重新调整头寸，墨西哥比索周三领跌新兴市场货币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/chip-stocks-sink-em-index-as-china-eyes-correction-territory</guid>
